    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Vanity of Volunteerism</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Linda F Willing letter says that</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Although I agree with Sara Mosle that individual volunteerism cannot take the place of necessary institutional change, she shouldn't discount the positive impact she has had on ''her'' kids. As Margaret Mead said: ''Never doubt that a small group of thoughtful, committed citizens can change the world. Indeed, it's the only thing that ever has.''</p>
        <p>Linda F. Willing  Lyons, Colo.</p>
      </block>
